OL,5, A 22-year-old Dundee bar manager who   
OL,6, was fired for being "too young" said   
OL,7, the experience "drove her to the       
OL,8, ground".                               
OL,10,FChristi Hurrell was awarded #18,583 in 
OL,11,Fcompensation after a tribunal ruled she
OL,12,Fwas wrongfully dismissed and           
OL,13,Fdiscriminated against due to her age.  
OL,15,FMs Hurrell took legal action after     
OL,16,Fbeing sacked in front of customers by  
OL,17,FSportsterz owner Scott Townshend.      
OL,19,FMr Townshend was contacted by the BBC  
OL,20,Ffor comment but did not respond.       
